Project Name:  
Smart Solar Tracking (Dual Axis) and Home Energy Management System

Components List:  
- 0.96" OLED Display (I2C, 128x64)  
- LDR Sensors – 4 pcs  
- Arduino Uno  
- Solar Panel – 2 pcs (2W, 6V each)  
- SG90 Servo Motors (180°, 4.8V) – 2 pcs (for dual axis) — 135/150tk each  
- TP4056 Charger (1A Li-ion) — 40tk  
- 18650 Battery (3.7V 2600mAh) — 450tk  
- *ACS712 Current Sensor
